text.tspan: In 1999, Tony teamed up with Activision to create the Tony Hawk’s Pro
Skater video game franchise. The Tony Hawk video game series
became one of the most popular game franchises in history and
continues to this day. His life would never be the same. In a stroke of
good timing, at the X Games that year, Tony also became the first
skateboarder to ever land a 900, a maneuver that had eluded (and
occasionally hobbled) him for 10 years . It was one of skating’s most
gripping moments, playing out in front of a collection of his peers and
fans, and on national TV. That exposure, along with his successful
video game, helped establish Tony’s mainstream celebrity.
